OL,4,Coffences against patients including
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FNathaniel Spencer, 38, of Quinton in
OL,8,FBirmingham, is charged with 15 counts
OL,9,Fof sexual assault; 17 counts of
OL,10,Fassault by penetration; nine counts of
OL,11,Fsexual assault of a child under 13;
OL,12,Fthree counts of assault of a child
OL,13,Funder 13 by penetration, and one count
OL,14,Fof attempting to assault by
OL,15,Fpenetration, the Crown Prosecution
OL,16,FService said.
