OL,7,FThe charges follow what Staffordshire
OL,8,FPolice called a "complex
OL,9,Finvestigation" into alleged sexual
OL,10,Foffences at the Royal Stoke University
OL,11,FHospital, in Stoke, and Russells Hall
OL,12,FHospital, in Dudley ` said to have
OL,13,Ftaken place between 2017 and 2021.
OL,15,FHe is due to appear at the North
OL,16,FStaffordshire Justice Centre on
OL,17,FJanuary 20.
