OL,7,FDr Paul Hudson, the medical director
OL,8,Fat the Dudley Group NHS Foundation
OL,9,FTrust, which manages Russells Hall
OL,10,FHospital, said: "We understand that
OL,11,Fmany of our patients, staff, and
OL,12,Fpeople in the wider community will
OL,13,Ffind this news very distressing.
OL,14,FAnyone with concerns or questions
OL,15,Fabout the care they have received in
OL,16,Four hospital should contact our
OL,17,Fdedicated helpline on 01384 322 311.
