OL,7,F"Our dedicated colleagues continue to
OL,8,Fsupport those affected by these
OL,9,Fissues, while cooperating with the
OL,10,Fpolice and relevant authorities in
OL,11,Ftheir investigations, throughout the
OL,12,Fprocess.
OL,14,F"Although we cannot comment on an
OL,15,Fongoing criminal process, we would
OL,16,Flike to reassure the public that the
OL,17,Fsafety and well-being of our patients
OL,18,Fand their relatives remains our
OL,19,Fhighest priority."
